Ctrl+Space - Selects the column

Shift+Space - Selects the row

Ctrl+Shift+"+" - Add row(s)/column(s) (Select a row/column and then press)

Ctrl + -  > Deletes the selected column(s)/row(s)

Ctrl+5 - Strike through

Alt += Sum column or row values

Alt+H+[BA/BN...] - All Borders/No Borders

Alt+H+BN - No Borders

Alt+H+[AC/AT/AM...] - Align Center/Align Top/Align Middle

Alt+H+MC - Merge Center

Alt+H then H+N - No Fill (removes the cell background color)

Alt+A+T - Filter Columns

Alt+A+C - Clear Filter Values

Alt+A+SA - Sort Ascending

Alt+A+SD - Sort Descending

Ctrl+V then Ctrl then V/F - To paste values/Formulas only

Ctrl+Shift+" (or) Ctrl+D - Copt top cell contents to current cell

Ctrl+; - Insert Current Date

Ctrl + Shift +: - Insert Current Time